<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>jạk ạ̉kwbyạn, nạẓw dkrmnjyạn</author>
<hymn_number>5860</hymn_number>
<title>bṣlạty lk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bṣlạty lk tnksr bdfỷ
 lạ̉mwạj fy dạkẖly

[V2]
 bṣlạty lk ysẖʿl lhyb nạrk klmạty

[V3]
 bṣlạty lk ynfjr qlby bḥbk kạlbrkạn

[V4]
 bṣlạty lk ydwy ạlṣmt fy ạ̉ʿmạqy

[V5]
 ḥyn ạ̉ṣly lk rby yhb ạlrwḥ fy qlby

[V6]
 ḥyn ạ̉ṣly rby tftḥ ạ̉bwạb ạlsmạwạt

[V7]
 wạ̉ry̱ bạlạ̹ymạn bạlrwḥ mạ lạ yry̱

[V8]
 ạ̉rạk ạ̉nt yạ kẖạlqy fạtḥạaⁿ ydyk mṣgẖyạaⁿ ạ̹ly</lyrics>
</song>